snippet.textDisplay: Finally! Home workouts! Inverted Chin curls and angel and devils are things i never would even think about trying because of some form of injury or ineffeciency, or even some sort of developed muscle dysmorphia from incorrect form. But i am starting to understand your philosophy with not just relying on these workouts specifically to get the results, but adding in more variety with so many options, being a body in a 3d space, and how the mentality of thinking that way can actually EFFECT your habits or rituals or whatever you want to call it, towards the end goal. I cannot stress enough, the mental benefit of trying these new motions on top or temporarily in place of a persons 'normal' routine. DUDE YOU ARE A GENIUS, in both how you have been presenting this program, and just how epicly effective it is. I have lost OVER 60Lbs of fat in the last 2 years, and i have been literally piling on so much muscle with just the crapton of energy so many of the exercises i have picked from your programs, i wish i could express how effective this program you have put together ACTUALLY IS. 1min- elevação pelvica com os pés na cadeira
